Package com.flipkart.bean

Class FlipfitAdmin

java.lang.Object
com.flipkart.bean.FlipfitAdmin
public class FlipfitAdmin extends Object
Represents an administrator in the FlipFit system. The admin has an ID, password, name, phone number, and email.
